definitions.definition: A percentage , a proportion (especially per hundred).
examples: only a small percent attain the top ranks

definitions.definition: One part per hundred ; one percent, hundredth .
An annuity or security with a certain fixed and guaranteed annual percentage rate of return or percentage dividend.
